To fulfill your request of adding a **cricket chirping sound** (tiếng dế kêu) when the timer completes, I will update the `TimerWidget.tsx` component.

I will replace the generic "bell" sound with a synthesized cricket sound using the Web Audio API. This will create a realistic "chirp-chirp" effect consisting of high-pitched pulses when the timer finishes.

